          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Products, Thorofare</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">New Jersey</ENAMEX>) and rotated for <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">20</NUMEX>
          <TIMEX TYPE="TIME">minutes</TIMEX> at <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">360</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">RPM</ENAMEX>. After shaking, we pipeted the eluted
          material from the petri <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">dish</ENAMEX> into a sterile microfuge
