          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">PCR</ENAMEX> products
          The <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">OL26</NUMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">OL27</ENAMEX> primer pair generates <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">a 388</TIMEX> base
          pair amplicon from a region of the <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">5</ENAMEX>' noncoding region of
