          OL26 and <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">JWA-1b</ENAMEX> generates an amplicon of <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">~292</NUMEX> base pairs
          from within the original amplicon. The <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">292 bp</NUMEX> amplicon
